DataElement.preferredName: Scientific Publication External Uniform Resource Identifier java.lang.Boolean
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A class of publication in which original scientific work is described.  The format usually includes an introduction in which relevant concepts are identified and the experimental system under study is presented, a section describing the experiments that were performed to test a specific hypothesis and the results and observations that were obtained, a section in which the results are discussed relative to findings by other investigators and the current state of knowledge in the field, and a section describing the experimental methods and procedures in sufficient detail to enable the reproduction of the work by independent investigators._Happening or arising or located outside or beyond some limits, or especially, some surface.:A character string that can identify any kind of resource on the Internet, including images, text, video, audio and programs.  The most commom type of a URI is a URL._Generic value domain for a primitive java datatype that is a Boolean value (true or false).
